{"word":"G3923 - παρεισφέρω - pareisphérō - par-ice-fer'-o - Give","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρεισφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pareisphérō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ice-fer'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வழங்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to bring in besides"},{"paragraph":"2. to contribute besides to something"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1533 - εἰσφέρω - eisphérō - ice-fer'-o/1533\">G1533</a>; to <i>bear in alongside</i>, that is, <i>introduce simultaneously:</i> - give.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}